title: Da Capo II: Imaginary Future
original_name: D.C.II ～ダ・カーポ II イマジナリーフューチャー～
sinopse: Due to family issues, Nanaka starts to stay in the Yoshino household, living together with Yoshiyuki and Sakura. In the same setting as the original D.C.II with a different story that revolves mainly around Nanaka and Koko.
